1:1 COMMENT "# text_protocol.z -- A user type that conforms to the `text` protocol"
1:70 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "# is a member of `StringLike` and can be passed to `print` (or any"
2:67 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# function generic over `StringLike`) without an explicit projection."
3:70 EOL "\n"
4:1 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# mylabel owns a string and exposes a stringview via the `text`"
5:64 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# protocol. Stored as a class because views cannot be aggregate"
6:64 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "# fields (doc/strings.pdoc) \u{2014} the owned string is the storage, the"
7:67 EOL "\n"
8:1 COMMENT "# view is produced on demand."
8:30 EOL "\n"
